---

<section id="about" class="chapter">
  <header class="chapter__head">
    <span class="chapter__num">04</span>
    <h2 class="chapter__title">About <em>me</em></h2>
    <p class="chapter__lede">Curious, playful, refreshing — and quietly obsessed with making data pipelines run clean.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: var(--s-8);">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p style="font-size: var(--t-md); line-height: var(--lh-loose); color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0 0 var(--s-5);">
        I'm a data operations professional who sits at the intersection of people, robots, and the data that trains them.
        From leading multi-hour teleoperation runs at Amazon Robotics to running enterprise demos for NVIDIA and Samsung at
        Skild AI — I specialize in the hands-on, high-stakes work that happens between the model and production.
      </p>
      <p style="font-size: var(--t-md); line-height: var(--lh-loose); color: var(--ink-soft); margin: 0;">
        I hold a B.S. in Management Information Systems from San Jose State University and I speak English, Hindi, Kannada,
        Tamil, and Spanish.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <div class="reveal-stagger" style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap: var(--s-3);">
        {[
          { label: 'Location',   value: 'San Francisco, CA' },
          { label: 'Status',     value: 'Open to Opportunities' },
          { label: 'Degree',     value: 'B.S. MIS — SJSU, 2025' },
          { label: 'Languages',  value: 'EN · HI · KN · TA · ES' },
          { label: 'Top stat',   value: '91% yield — #1 in Q1 2026' },
          { label: 'Companies',  value: 'Amazon · DeepMind · Skild AI' },
        ].map(stat => (
          <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns: 120px 1fr; gap: var(--s-4); border-top: 1px dashed var(--ink-faint); padding-top: var(--s-3);">
            <span style="font-family: var(--f-mono); font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-mute);">{stat.label}</span>
            <span style="font-size: var(--t-base); font-weight: 600; color: var(--ink);">{stat.value}</span>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    section > div[class="grid"] {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
